DXG TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 38.21% to NT$154,086,000 from NT$249,361,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            154,086          249,361    
YOY%             -38.21%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            542,670          648,367    
YOY%             -16.30% 
=================================================================
 